    <title>预备知识</title>
    <link href="/2025/02/28/%E9%A2%84%E5%A4%87%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/"/>
    <url>/2025/02/28/%E9%A2%84%E5%A4%87%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>计划研一下学期，仔细研读《广义函数与函数空间导论》，预期达到：对常用的经典的函数空间的基本性质有较为系统和深入的了解，较为熟练的掌握广义函数的基本性质。</p><h1 id="预备知识">预备知识</h1><h2 id="lebesgue-lp-空间">Lebesgue <spanclass="math inline">\(L^p\)</span> 空间</h2><h2 id="卷积与young不等式">卷积与Young不等式</h2><h2 id="分布函数-d_falpha-与弱-lp-空间">分布函数 <spanclass="math inline">\(d_f(\alpha)\)</span> 与弱 <spanclass="math inline">\(L^p\)</span> 空间</h2><div class="definition"><p>(分布函数<span class="math inline">\(d_f(\alpha)\)</span>) 设<spanclass="math inline">\(f\)</span>是测度空间<spanclass="math inline">\((X,\mu)\)</span>上的可测函数，其分布函数<spanclass="math inline">\(d_f(\alpha)\)</span>定义于<spanclass="math inline">\([0,\infty)\)</span>上，满足 <spanclass="math inline">\(d_f(\alpha):=\mu(\{x\in X \mid|f(x)|&gt;\alpha\})\)</span>.</p></div>]]></content>
    
    
